me.archdukeliamus.dygenerate - package me.archdukeliamus.dygenerate
The me.archdukeliamus.dygenerate package describes the Dygenerate utility for inserting invokedynamic (indy) and dynamic constant (condy) ldc opcodes into Java (or any other JVM language) source code.

P

patchSurrogateReferences(byte[], Map<Surrogate, BootstrapData>) - Static method in class me.archdukeliamus.dygenerate.Dygenerate
Patch references to surrogate methods in the provided class using the provided surrogate map, removing any surrogate methods present and substituting in invokedynamic and ldc instructions in the place of surrogate method invocations.
